{"name":"Transfert de vie","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/hands-circle-light-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Vous sacrifiez une partie de votre santé pour soigner les blessures d'une autre créature. Vous subissez 4d8 points de dégâts nécrotiques, que vous ne pouvez pas réduire par quelconque moyen, et une créature de votre choix, que vous pouvez voir et qui se trouve à portée, gagne une quantité de points de vie égale au double des dégâts nécrotiques que vous subissez.</p>\n<p><strong>À plus haut niveau. </strong>Si vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 4 ou plus, la quantité de dégâts reçus augmente de 1d8 par niveau au-delà du troisième.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":9,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["4d8","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"3UjVNZPJLHwgrlkI":3},"flags":{"mre-dnd5e":{"formulaGroups":[{"label":"Primaire","formulaSet":[0]}],"autoRollDamage":true},"enhanced-terrain-layer":{"multiple":null,"elevation":null,"depth":null,"environment":""},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rfwMYkBU3GuFy1bE"}},"_id":"OmLBTZfu1XtAiMFS"}
{"_id":"RnK1xJyi0BZ4mKWr","name":"Envoi de message","type":"spell","img":"icons/sundries/documents/envelope-stealed-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Vous envoyez un court message d'au maximum vingt-cinq mots à une créature qui vous est familière. Elle entend le message dans son esprit, sait que c'est vous qui le lui avez envoyé si elle vous connaît, et peut vous répondre immédiatement de la même manière. Le sort permet aux créatures dotées d'une Intelligence supérieure ou égale à 1 de comprendre le sens de votre message.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez envoyer votre message à n'importe quelle distance, et même sur un autre plan d'existence, mais il y a 5 % de chances, si la cible est sur un autre plan, que le message ne lui parvienne pas.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature","range":{"value":"illimitée"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"Un petit bout de fil de cuivre","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"price":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"3UjVNZPJLHwgrlkI":3},"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"